1.	Comply strictly with the provisions of COA Circular No. 97-002 and JMC 2015-01 on the grant, utilization and liquidation of cash advances;
2.	Require the accountable officers to liquidate the overdue cash advances. Invoke the provisions of law authorizing the withholding of salary of personnel who unjustifiably fails to settle his/her cash advances within the prescribed period;
