We recommended the following:
The Municipal Engineer coordinate with the department concerned to fast track the implementation of the projects;
The Local Chief Executive shall ensure compliance with the responsibilities provided for in paragraph 5.0 of DILG and DBM Joint Circular No. 2017-1 to achieve desirable socio-economic development and environmental outcomes;
The Local Development Council monitor the implementation of the projects as incorporated in the Annual Investment Plan; and
Management incorporate projects in the Annual Invest Plan that is within the scope allowable as identified in social development, economic development and environmental management.

